&lt;p&gt;VMware Fusion（for mac）：&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudm13YXJlLmNvbS9wcm9kdWN0cy9mdXNpb24uaHRtbA==&#34;&gt;https://www.vmware.com/products/fusion.html&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
